{"tid":1462854,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"話你知8.18 遊行人數嘅重要性","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T01:33:27.000Z","uid":87915,"like":94,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"07cec02f326ea32ed98b1cffa3501f6588406fbc","tid":1462854,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:27:11.000Z","msg":"其實相信大家都知<br />\n<br />\n經過兩個月抗爭，塞鐵、圍警署、片地開花集會遊行、汽油彈、三罷、空管罷工、醫護集會、機場停飛<br />\n<br />\n所有影響民生經濟嘅事件發生之後<br />\n<br />\n一個非常重要指標，仲有幾多和理非嘅人支持<br />\n<br />\n得三十萬？ 定仲係二百萬人？ 甚至更多人支持？<br />\n<br />\n請各位文宣  勇武  和理非  <br />\n不論最終 有冇不反對通知書<br />\n放低你所有手頭活動 谷爆佢<br />\n動之以情好，跪求好<br />\n<br />\n請8.18 再嚟多次超級大遊行"},{"pid":"5ee2ed461b013bd8dba55645dc2260910cc6d235","tid":1462854,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ecb1336d6423138f9e9c4fa3a16e28b5a304d2e","tid":1462854,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e709029dd4b0e8d8afa6b75502e3fd6415d86219","tid":1462854,"uid":263973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:40:14.000Z","msg":"用 818 取代推"},{"pid":"03bfe58adb2d109c55a1d827af131263195c5683","tid":1462854,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:42:41.000Z","msg":"8.18"},{"pid":"99d3c3cc4b235c939566401d5615455f3256c100","tid":1462854,"uid":78184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:43:47.000Z","msg":"和理非818"},{"pid":"fcff596dd256346ee59490c0eca7770fb9391bf6","tid":1462854,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:44:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f86088d3c22ca522b98ffc675c6180a5a9e22ab","tid":1462854,"uid":42554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"a0c91c703f0c3c2d8a35a37110a6ace5b5718d10","tid":1462854,"uid":72994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi